# Observability & auditability

- Use structured logging (structlog). Never log secrets or raw credentials.
- Preserve audit events for sensitive actions; keep usage metering and quota accounting intact.
- Record provider provenance and fallback status; surface degraded states, don't hide them.
- Any new sensitive path must be observable and auditable (who, what, when, idempotency key).
